  simpa [UnboundedDiscOffset] using hunb

/-- Variant of `not_boundedDiscrepancy_of_unboundedDiscOffset` with the step-size side condition
written as `1 Ôëñ d`.

Many later stages prefer `1 Ôëñ d` to avoid rewriting `d > 0`.
